[node name="RagdollSkeleton" type="Node3D"]
script = ExtResource("1_ragdoll")

[node name="Info" type="Node" parent="."]
editor_description = "Ragdoll Skeleton for BattleZone Party characters.
This scene provides a pre-configured physics skeleton that can be
dynamically spawned and attached to any PlayerCharacter.

The skeleton uses simplified joint configurations optimized for:
- Fun, exaggerated physics
- Mobile performance (<1ms per ragdoll)
- Network synchronization efficiency

To use: Instance this scene and call setup(character_node) or
let the RagdollSystem auto-generate the skeleton."

